{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getHomeDir"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As with most UNIX tools, this function will return the value of the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"HOME","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" environment variable if it is set to an existing absolute path","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"name, falling back to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"passwd"},{"type":"text","text":" file in the case that it is unset."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the path given in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HOME"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-absolute, does not exist, or is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"not a directory, the result is undefined.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Before version 2.36 this function would ignore the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HOME"},{"type":"text","text":" environment"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"variable, taking the value from the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"passwd"},{"text":" database instead. This was","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changed to increase the compatibility of GLib with other programs (and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the XDG basedir specification) and to increase testability of programs","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"based on GLib (by making it easier to run them from test frameworks)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your program has a strong requirement for either the new or the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"old behaviour (and if you don’t wish to increase your GLib"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dependency to ensure that the new behaviour is in effect) then you"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"should either directly check the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HOME"},{"text":" environment variable yourself","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"or unset it before calling any functions in GLib."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/gethomedir()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/getHomeDir()"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"getHomeDir()","externalID":"s:4GLib10getHomeDirSSSgyF","roleHeading":"Function","symbolKind":"func","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getHomeDir","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Gets the current user’s home directory.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/glib","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","type":"topic"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/getHomeDir()":{"abstract":[{"text":"Gets the current user’s home directory.","type":"text"}],"title":"getHomeDir()","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/getHomeDir()","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/gethomedir()","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getHomeDir","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}